A shared refrigerator offered by Alibaba's Hema Fresh brand debuts in Shanghai over the weekend, with an aim to provide food and other daily goods late at night. Hema's staff will re-fill the refrigerator from 9:30 pm to 10 pm. Any products that haven't been sold will be donated to charities. Photo: IC  Newspaper headline: Sharing economy 
